## Understanding Threats

Critical infrastructure faces various types of threats:

- State-sponsored Actors
- Cybercriminal Organizations
- Hacktivists
- Insider Threats
- Natural Disasters

## Threat Assessment

A systematic approach to evaluating threats includes:

- Threat Identification
- Vulnerability Analysis
- Risk Assessment
- Impact Analysis
- Mitigation Strategies

